FBIS4-27921 "dreas109__a94023" FBIS-EAS-94-109-A Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 ANNEX North Korea Envoy Threatens To `Formally Withdraw' From NPT Envoy Threatens To `Formally Withdraw' From NPT OW0306042594 Tokyo MAINICHI SHIMBUN in Japanese 3 Jun 94 Morning Edition p 7--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW0306042594 Tokyo MAINICHI SHIMBUN Japanese BFN [Text] Vienna, 2 May (KYODO) -- Councilor Yun Ho-chin of the DPRK (North Korean) Embassy in Vienna stated the following on 2 June: We will have to formally withdraw from the Nuclear Nonproliferation Treaty (NPT) if the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) continues to demand inspections according to its security measures (nuclear inspections) agreement.
